# STEPS FOR FIRST CLONES #

- Change app's name
- Change git remote origin to avoid push/pull conflicts
- Change config.action_mailer.default_url_options in "/config/environments/production.rb"
- Change Mailer @base url in "/app/mailers/application_mailer.rb"
- Add icon.png in "/app/assets/images"
- Set Up Mailer SMTP with Username and password in .end file



Versioning:
$ rails generate versionist:new_controller <name> <module namespace>
$ rails generate versionist:new_controller v2 V2